{"tid":1186124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門係咁閃電","createTime":"2019-06-04T17:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T17:29:06.000Z","uid":5618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4b3bdda727ed96800dd5a36f7b3cc50e318c15","tid":1186124,"uid":5618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"閃左半個鐘都有，但未落雨"},{"pid":"bbcf24691d53d291c0ac21d1505835a4e1c703f5","tid":1186124,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"上水都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136407b3c18024ee95d0716dcc57b2cac27f2bc4","tid":1186124,"uid":57388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"香港仔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b314b31702164512a7537aa792e49a2a9931c24d","tid":1186124,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbcf24691d53d291c0ac21d1505835a4e1c703f5","tid":1186124,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"上水都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"上水冇事喎"},{"pid":"658eae426b2ee673cab6a24c609ed43e29a3ee84","tid":1186124,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"咁又點撚樣"},{"pid":"9afb3b27dcbef8a0218609b7359287f27b17f29a","tid":1186124,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"旱天雷"},{"pid":"2bc4480d623238ca93218c33831df131c0d534db","tid":1186124,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9afb3b27dcbef8a0218609b7359287f27b17f29a","tid":1186124,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"旱天雷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"第二十五卦：无妄卦(天雷无妄)<br />\n<br />\n  无妄。元亨利贞。其匪正有眚，不利有攸往。<br />\n<br />\n  象曰：天下雷行，物与无妄。先王以茂对时，育万物。<br />\n<br />\n  白话文解释<br />\n<br />\n  无妄卦：嘉美通泰，卜问得吉兆。行为不正当，则有灾殃，有所往则不利。<br />\n<br />\n  《象辞》说：本卦上卦为乾为天，下卦为震为雷，天宇之下，春雷滚动，万物萌发，孳生繁衍，这是无妄的卦象。先王观此卦象，从而奋勉努力，顺应时令，保育万物。<br />\n<br />\n  邵雍河洛理数解卦<br />\n<br />\n  不欺不妄，真实至诚;顺乎自然，福禄深宏。<br />\n<br />\n  小吉：得此卦者，顺其自然，守正道者，诸事皆宜。但行为不检者，必招灾祸。"}]}